Package: syrona
Type: Package
Title: Stratified Prevalence Comparison Across OMOP CDM Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Maarja", "Pajusalu", email = "maarja@maarjapajusalu.ee",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Extracts stratified prevalence tables from OMOP CDM databases
    (conditions, procedures, drugs), computes log2 prevalence ratios between
    paired datasets, and synthesizes them via random-effects meta-analysis
    at multiple aggregation levels (year, age group, sex).
